page.title: 11NEWBIGGIN/MY HOUSE
page.content: SOME HOUSES ARE MADE OF STONES .SOME HOUSES ARE PEBBLEDASH AND BRICKS. SOME OF THE HOUSES ARE JUST BRICK HOUSES.SOME HOUSES ARE DIFFERENT COLOURS LIKE ORANGE.SOMETIMES UNDERNEATH THE PEBBLEDASH THERE IS BREEZEBLOCK .SOME HOUSES HAVE GOT A WINDOW IN THE ROOF. SOME HOUSES HAVE RED/TILES,BLACK/TILES,ORANGE/TILES OR GREY/TILES ON THEIR ROOF,S. SINCE THE WAR, ARCHITECTS HAVE GIVEN A GREAT DEAL OF THOUGHT TO THE DESIGN OF SMALL HOUSE,S AND SOME OF THEM ARE VERY COMFORTABL TO LIVE IN. THERE ARE 45 CHILDREN LIVING IN TERRACED HOUSES.13 IN SEMI/DETACHED HOUSES.4 DETACHED HOUSES.
